{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id8f530e45-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s2151h"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2151h"},"text":"§ 2151h.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Cost-sharing","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"No assistance shall be furnished by the United States Government to a country under sections 2151a through 2151d of this title until the country provides assurances to the President, and the President is satisfied, that such country will provide at least 25 per centum of the costs of the entire program, project, or activity with respect to which such assistance is to be furnished, except that such costs borne by such country may be provided on an “inkind” basis.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id8f530e46-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/195"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–195","children":[],"tail":", pt. I, § 110, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/189/s2/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–189, § 2(3)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1973-12-17"},"text":"Dec. 17, 1973","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/87/716"},"text":"87 Stat. 716","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/161/tIII/s307"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–161, title III, § 307","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1975-12-20"},"text":"Dec. 20, 1975","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/89/859"},"text":"89 Stat. 859","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/88/tI/s106"},"text":"Pub. L. 95–88, title I, § 106","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1977-08-03"},"text":"Aug. 3, 1977","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/91/535"},"text":"91 Stat. 535","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/424/tI/s112/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 95–424, title I, § 112(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1978-10-06"},"text":"Oct. 6, 1978","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/92/949"},"text":"92 Stat. 949","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/83/tXII/s1211/a/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–83, title XII, § 1211(a)(3)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1985-08-08"},"text":"Aug. 8, 1985","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/99/279"},"text":"99 Stat. 279","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id8f530e47-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id8f530e48-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id8f530e49-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1985—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/83"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–83","children":[],"tail":" struck out subsec. (a) designation, and struck out subsec. (b) which set forth funding limits for grant assistance under sections 2151a to 2151d of this title."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1978—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/424"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–424","children":[],"tail":" struck out provision, following “on an ‘in-kind’ basis”, relating to waiver by the President of cost-sharing requirement in case of a project or activity in a country determined to be relatively least developed by the agency primarily responsible for administering subchapter I of this chapter."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/424"},"text":"Pub. L. 95–424","children":[],"tail":" substituted “No” for “Except for grants to countries determined to be relatively least developed based on the United Nations Conference on Trade and Development list of ‘relatively least developed countries’, no”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1977—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/88/s106/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 95–88, § 106(1)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “sections 2151a through 2151d” for “sections 2151a through 2151e”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/88/s106/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 95–88, § 106(2)","children":[],"tail":", inserted provisions creating an exception for grants to countries determined to be relatively least developed based on the United Nations Conference on Trade and Development list of “relatively least developed countries” and substituted “sections 2151a through 2151d” for “sections 2151a through 2151e”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1975—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/161"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–161","children":[],"tail":" authorized Presidential waiver of cost-sharing as a condition for being furnished project or activity assistance in the case of a relatively least developed country."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id8f530e4a-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"id8f530e4b-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References to Sections 2151a Through 2151d Deemed To Include Section 2293","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"References to sections 2151a through 2151d of this title are deemed to include a reference to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2293"},"text":"section 2293 of this title","children":[],"tail":". See "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2293/d/1"},"text":"section 2293(d)(1) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"id8f530e4c-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 1985 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/83"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–83","children":[],"tail":" effective "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1985-10-01"},"text":"Oct. 1, 1985","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/83/s1301"},"text":"section 1301 of Pub. L. 99–83","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2151–1"},"text":"section 2151–1 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"id8f530e4d-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 1978 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/424"},"text":"Pub. L. 95–424","children":[],"tail":" effective "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1978-10-01"},"text":"Oct. 1, 1978","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/424/s605"},"text":"section 605 of Pub. L. 95–424","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2151"},"text":"section 2151 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"execDoc","id":"id8f530e4e-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Executive Documents","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"delegationOfFunctions","id":"id8f530e4f-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Delegation of Functions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For delegation of functions of President under this section, see Ex. Ord. No. 12163, ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1979-09-29"},"text":"Sept. 29, 1979","children":[],"tail":", 44 F.R. 56673, as amended, set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2381"},"text":"section 2381 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
